---
// src/components/Traceability.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-0">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-edurun-purple text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-purple-400 opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-purple-500"></span>
          </span>
          Monitoreo Activo
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-edurun-dark mb-6">
          Evalúe el proceso,<br>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue to-edurun-purple">no solo el resultado.</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          A diferencia de una entrega tradicional, Edurun registra cada interacción. Detecte patrones sospechosos o valide el esfuerzo genuino con métricas detalladas.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded bg-edurun-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs">1</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Historial de Ejecuciones:</strong> Vea cuántas veces el alumno probó su código antes de enviarlo.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded bg-edurun-purple text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs">2</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Alertas de Integridad:</strong> Registros automáticos de intentos de copiar/pegar o cambios de ventana.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded bg-gray-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs">3</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Tiempos de Foco:</strong> Sepa exactamente cuánto tiempo estuvo el estudiante trabajando activamente.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue to-edurun-purple rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
        
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
          
          <div class="bg-gray-900 px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-mono">reporte_alumno_final.edurun</div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6 border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase font-semibold">Estudiante</h4>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Benjamin Nuñez</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                  Aprobado (100/100)
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Ejecuciones</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-edurun-blue">12</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Tests Pasados</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-edurun-purple">5/5</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Tiempo Total</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-700">5m 50s</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h5 class="text-red-800 font-semibold text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
                Registro de Actividad Sospechosa
              </h5>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm text-red-700 bg-white p-2 rounded border border-red-100 shadow-sm">
                  <span>Salió de pantalla completa</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs opacity-75">09:38:29</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm text-gray-600 bg-white p-2 rounded border border-gray-100">
                  <span>Intento de pegar (Ctrl+V) bloqueado</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs opacity-75">09:40:12</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>